Company Name: Name of the company for which employee turnover rate is being tracked
Quarter: The quarter of the year for which employee turnover rate is being reported (e.g. Q1, Q2, Q3, Q4)
Year: The year for which employee turnover rate is being reported
Employee Turnover Rate: The percentage of employees who left the company during the quarter
Change from Previous Quarter: The percentage change in employee turnover rate from the previous quarter
